  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the difference of three vaginal estrogens creams comparative with placebo on
      improvement of hormonal cytology, local and systemic climacteric complaints, as well as its
      endometrial security.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
