  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  post menopause women

          -  normal oncotic cytology and mammogram

          -  any grade of pelvic organ prolapse with surgery indication and ultrasound with
             endometrium measure less than 5 mm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  vaginal bleeding

          -  hormonal replacement on the past three months

          -  renal or hepatic desease

          -  porfiria

          -  past venous thromboembolism; ulcerated prolapse
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
